## Notes

This document is intended as a **supplement** to the  
**Aether Galaxy Foundational Guidebook (AGFG)** and may evolve with future revisions.  
It is a technical standard within the fiction of the setting —  
the Bureau of Astrogation’s manual for how the Commonwealth keeps its galaxy organized.

> *No canon; only coherence.*
